        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stopping Consumption of Tobacco by Teens Act of 2019 or the</b> <b>SCOTT Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the sale or distribution of a tobacco product to any person under 21 years of age. The bill also establishes age verification requirements for remote sales (including online sales) of vaping products such as e-cigarettes.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
